@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.cos(v1 + 0.28)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(0.21) + v0)
    tmp = v0
    tmp = wp.sin(((v0 + 0.17 / tmp + 0.57) - (tmp + 0.90 + v0 + 0.24)))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v2 + 0.93 + tmp + 0.12)))
    data[tid] = v0
